Battera::

she sighed as he took off without her. Again. She was getting tired 
oe being left behind. She transformed into bat mode and followed 
CyberShark. "Your not going off again and leaving me to just sit back 
and worry about you. I'm coming along this time. And no, I"m not 
going to debate with you on this. I'm coming and that's final."


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "dachande" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::Dark Prime::
> 
>     He reached the Council base and looked for people.
> 
> ::Magmatron/Cerberus/Dachande/Jynx/Obitus/AEger/
> Fame/Bellum/Neamen Hydra/Eclipse/Wolveritron::
> 
>     They all followed the signal's of Magnus and Valtron to aid the 
bot known as Kit Kat. Magmatron was only helping to win over trust, 
and his Destrons were only following orders. Dachande was a Destron, 
so he had to follow, he told Battera that he had to help, gave her a 
quick kiss and ran off. Eclipse and Wolveritron went to test out 
their new abilities.
